title: Congressman Calls Donald Trump’s SNL Gig ‘A Huge Corporate Blunder’
text: When Donald Trump hosts Saturday Night Live on November 7, NBC might well end up toasting a ratings windfall for the iconic sketch television show. But if some prominent voices have their way, the GOP frontrunner will see his guest host spot scrapped without even so much as setting foot inside Studio 8H at 30...
